<.shell title="Privacy policy" eyebrow="Last updated May 26, 2026">
  <p class="lead text-lg/8 text-olive-700">
    Maraithon is an operational tool for busy humans. We collect as little as possible to make it
    work, store it securely, and never sell it. This page describes exactly what we collect, why,
    and how to remove it.
  </p>

  <h2 class="mt-12 font-display text-3xl text-olive-950">Who we are</h2>
  <p class="mt-3">
    Maraithon is operated by ArgoNavis Inc., a Delaware corporation with offices in Toronto and
    San Francisco. Our registered address is 1111B S Governors Ave STE 3699, Dover, DE 19904, USA.
    You can reach us at
    <a href="mailto:support@maraithon.com" class="underline">support@maraithon.com</a>
    for any privacy-related question or request.
  </p>

  <h2 class="mt-10 font-display text-3xl text-olive-950">What we collect</h2>
  <p class="mt-3">We collect three categories of data:</p>
  <ol class="mt-3 list-decimal space-y-3 pl-6">
    <li>
      <strong>Account data.</strong>
      Your email address, used to sign you in via magic link and to contact you about your account.
      We do not store passwords because Maraithon does not use them.
    </li>
    <li>
      <strong>Content you create.</strong>
      Todos, contacts, chat messages, and notes you add to Maraithon. These are owned by you and stored
      so the app can show them back to you on any device.
    </li>
    <li>
      <strong>Connected data.</strong>
      When you connect an integration (Gmail, Google Calendar, Slack, Linear, Notion, GitHub, etc.),
      Maraithon reads the data needed to power your agents. We store OAuth tokens encrypted at rest,
      and we cache only the data required to surface what needs your attention.
    </li>
  </ol>

  <h2 class="mt-10 font-display text-3xl text-olive-950">What we do not collect</h2>
  <ul class="mt-3 list-disc space-y-2 pl-6">
    <li>We do not sell or rent your data to anyone.</li>
    <li>We do not use your data to train third-party AI models.</li>
    <li>We do not track you across other websites or apps.</li>
    <li>We do not run third-party advertising or marketing analytics on you.</li>
  </ul>

  <h2 class="mt-10 font-display text-3xl text-olive-950">How we use it</h2>
  <p class="mt-3">We use what we collect only to:</p>
  <ul class="mt-3 list-disc space-y-2 pl-6">
    <li>Authenticate you and keep your session live.</li>
    <li>Run the agents you create and send you the results.</li>
    <li>Send transactional email about your account (sign-in links, security alerts).</li>
    <li>Operate, maintain, and improve the service.</li>
    <li>Comply with legal obligations.</li>
  </ul>

  <h2 class="mt-10 font-display text-3xl text-olive-950">Where it lives</h2>
  <p class="mt-3">
    Account and content data is stored in a PostgreSQL database hosted on
    <a href="https://fly.io" class="underline" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Fly.io</a>
    in the Toronto (YYZ) region. We use the following sub-processors:
  </p>
  <ul class="mt-3 list-disc space-y-2 pl-6">
    <li><strong>Fly.io</strong> — application hosting and database.</li>
    <li><strong>OpenAI</strong> — large language model inference for agent reasoning.</li>
    <li><strong>Postmark</strong> — transactional email delivery (sign-in links).</li>
    <li><strong>Sentry</strong> — error monitoring (no personal content is logged).</li>
  </ul>
  <p class="mt-3">
    Each sub-processor has contractual obligations to protect your data and is bound by their own
    privacy policies. Connected integrations (Google, Slack, Linear, etc.) operate under their own
    terms; Maraithon only requests the OAuth scopes needed for the agents you set up.
  </p>

  <h2 class="mt-10 font-display text-3xl text-olive-950">How long we keep it</h2>
  <p class="mt-3">
    We retain your account and content for as long as your account is active. If you delete your
    account, we delete account data, content, and connected-integration tokens within 30 days.
    Anonymous aggregate logs may be retained longer for service reliability.
  </p>

  <h2 class="mt-10 font-display text-3xl text-olive-950">Your rights</h2>
  <p class="mt-3">No matter where you live, you can:</p>
  <ul class="mt-3 list-disc space-y-2 pl-6">
    <li>Request a copy of the personal data we hold about you.</li>
    <li>Correct any data that is inaccurate or out of date.</li>
    <li>Delete your account and all associated data.</li>
    <li>Disconnect any integration at any time, which revokes the related OAuth token.</li>
    <li>Withdraw consent to processing at any time.</li>
  </ul>
  <p class="mt-3">
    Email <a href="mailto:support@maraithon.com" class="underline">support@maraithon.com</a>
    and we&rsquo;ll act on it within 30 days.
  </p>

  <h2 class="mt-10 font-display text-3xl text-olive-950">Deleting your account</h2>
  <p class="mt-3">
    You can delete your account in either the iOS app (Settings &rarr; Account &rarr; Delete account)
    or by emailing <a href="mailto:support@maraithon.com" class="underline">support@maraithon.com</a>
    from the address on file. Deletion is permanent and removes your todos, contacts, chat history,
    OAuth tokens, and account record from our production database. Backups roll forward and are
    purged within 30 days.
  </p>

  <h2 class="mt-10 font-display text-3xl text-olive-950">Children</h2>
  <p class="mt-3">
    Maraithon is not directed at children under 13 (or the equivalent age in your jurisdiction).
    We do not knowingly collect data from children. If you believe a child has provided us data,
    contact us and we&rsquo;ll delete it.
  </p>

  <h2 class="mt-10 font-display text-3xl text-olive-950">Security</h2>
  <p class="mt-3">
    Data is encrypted in transit (TLS) and at rest. OAuth tokens are encrypted at the application
    layer with rotating keys. We follow standard secure-development practices and run automated
    dependency audits. Security incidents that affect you will be disclosed without undue delay.
  </p>

  <h2 class="mt-10 font-display text-3xl text-olive-950">Changes to this policy</h2>
  <p class="mt-3">
    If we make material changes to this policy, we&rsquo;ll notify you by email and update the
    &ldquo;Last updated&rdquo; date above before the changes take effect.
  </p>

  <h2 class="mt-10 font-display text-3xl text-olive-950">Contact</h2>
  <p class="mt-3">
    Questions, requests, or concerns:
    <a href="mailto:support@maraithon.com" class="underline">support@maraithon.com</a>.
  </p>
</.shell>
